According to his confession he had to choose pensions and restaurants.
He asked for an invoice for the drinks, along the lines of these invoices were then prepared to be sent to the competition notices, among others, to those of the Ministry of Youth and Sport, the Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs and the City of Budapest.
